parameters: 【Masamune】The door is locked.
【Masamune】The door is locked.
【Masamune】It doesn't react even if I ride it...
【Masamune】It doesn't react even if I ride it...

I made a switch with a hardness that even a cat
can't press to hide important things for myself.

But it's too hard that I can't even step on it
myself. If I want to press it, the only option
would be to drop something heavy on top of it.
The Diary of Vermeer Wilford

I was able to catch Photon Graphpard and expel
them.

I should be able to feel at ease, but is that
really the case?

He was skilled in transformation magic... No,
maybe I'm overthinking. Let's forget about it.

I made a passage connecting the girls' dormitory
for Chachamaru and Coco. Now we can meet anytime.

Both of them are really happy. That alone is
enough.

The entrance was made in my room. It's a magic
circle that only Chachamaru can open, so it's
reassuring.

But what should we do from next year onwards? If
our existence is exposed, the passage might be
destroyed.

I could use a spell that makes this room less
desirable. That way, it will remain vacant and
hopefully go unnoticed.

I will also cast a barrier spell just in case
someone intrudes.

To undo the barrier magic, there is no choice but
for me to cast the spell I created.

To ensure that no one finds out, I will store the
grimoire here.

And by the way, let's make sure not to forget the
password for the treasure vault. The password is
'curiosity killed the cat'.

【Masamune】 This person wrote the password and how
to unlock it in their diary, but they're too
careless...

【Masamune】 So this is the grimoire... They're a
good person, but not very smart it seems.
【Masamune】 I'll make sure to remember it.

I've become able to use the Rock Barrier
Destruction Magic!

【Tommy】 By the way, this passage was a secret
route for Chachamaru and Coco to meet, huh?
【Tommy】 The person who made it is a good person.

【Masamune】 That's right. Let's learn from this and
have Skeleton Head change their ways too.
【Skeleton Head】 Not yet. I won't give up.

【Skeleton Head】 Every man has a perverted heart.
Let's explore until the end!
【Leon】 Oh well...
